    <title>Network Search</title>
    
    <p>
    <app>Modem Manager GUI</app> can be used to search available mobile networks.
    Click on the <gui style="button">Scan</gui> button in the toolbar.
    </p>
    
    <figure>
        <title>Network search window of <app>Modem Manager GUI</app>.</title>
        <media type="image" mime="image/png" src="figures/scan-window.png"/>
    </figure>
    
    <p>
    If one mobile network appears more than once in the list, this mobile
    network use different broadcasting standards. It is obvioius that you
    can't scan mobile networks using broadcasting standards that your modem
    doesn't support.
    </p>
      
